 the smoke is like a thick yet mellow drift of pine wood burning and a smell that triggers you memory centre an...â€

â€œThis is my all time favorite strain. As a dying person does, I happen to have alot of health issues and this is the best for all of them. column3: â€œChernobyl is a staple for our patients and for us personally. One of the few we always keep handy. Great day time med, allows you to keep going about your business. â€œThe zip of Chernobyl I got was entirely made up of crazy dense nugs. The bugs gave off a prominently citrus smell and, when ground, formed a fluffy and sticky pile. The high sneaks up quickly and provides a heady wired feeling perfect for getting up and active. Delicious weed all aroundâ€
â€œVery smooth smoke, not harsh at all despite it's pungent aroma. Nice high, very functional.â€
